		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Your magic came to you seemingly at random. Whether the result of magical experimentation, a gift from a chaotic entity, or even appearing out of nowhere, your magic is chaotic and unpredictable. Some wild mages are spotted at a young age, whereas others discover their volatile magic when they're older. A wild mage's spells always have a chance to do something random. Usually this is a good thing, but accidents do happen.</p><p>In the world of Elkan, wild magic is the domain of Baphomet, the wild minotaur god.</p><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>The Wild Mage</caption><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.yXSOvWE0v2BWMshU]{Random Wild Surge}</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.QqUWmLamy78Eu1dC]{Avert Disaster}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Cjd9KZdWZd7lum2H]{Voluntary Surge}</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.X04dCtqgA13slfdC]{Delayed Surge}</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Be3OL8Ulw5y3PAqZ]{Chaos Conductor}</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.TC9Pv4NRHoZ0pYtT]{Magical Blowout}</td></tr></tbody></table><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>Expanded Spell List</caption><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Sorcerer Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Extra Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.EBXbuU6UgNza87rc]{Chromatic Orb}</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.gOxZm4XAYTyrlGBo]{Prismatic Bolt}</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.BnfcbtYsHn4lyXML]{Blink}</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.qiyNsnKP